The .rdl file failed to upload to Power BI Service with 
error code rsWrongNumberOfTablixCells.

This means the tablix has a mismatch between the number 
of cells in the header row and the number of cells in 
the detail row.

Please fix the .rdl file by doing the following.
Count the number of TablixColumn elements in the 
TablixColumns section.
Make sure the header row has exactly that many TablixCell 
elements.
Make sure the detail row has exactly that many TablixCell 
elements.
Every TablixColumn must have a corresponding TablixCell 
in both the header row and the detail row.
No more, no less.
Rewrite the corrected .rdl file to disk and confirm 
the filename.

